The paper proposes a novel component for improving image and video recognition tasks by efficiently capturing long-range relations. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves attention mechanisms, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM) research. Finally, the paper also mentions the efficiency of the proposed method, which could be relevant to the neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category.
